{"tid":1217923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中共科技] 我喺咪俾人鈎左線","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T14:54:46.000Z","uid":97383,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"93847f3793433403fda9c3d2dc08b9b1e96b72db","tid":1217923,"uid":97383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"我尋日晏晝發左個夢 打俾個喺金鐘嘅fd<br />\n<br />\n正常電話接通緊嘅時候應該會有「嘟嘟」咁嘅接駁鈴聲<br />\n但我打俾佢之後就直接聽到有兩把講普通話既女人聲 冇左應有嘅「嘟嘟」聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢講咩我唔係聽得好清楚 我呢面係咁喂佢都冇反應<br />\n<br />\n之後我cut左佢線 再打多次比我個fd<br />\n佢竟然話頭先果個電話佢聽到我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我完全聽唔到佢講野 佢亦都聽唔到果個女人講野<br />\n<br />\n唔知會唔會真係被監聽 或者係有咩原因大家可以討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲小心啲<br />\n<br />\n利申 用支那移動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7eb28c1df5880f468ffa0326d2d1ba05096db6c","tid":1217923,"uid":38953,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"轉台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e243bbdad0f62804de138337cd9e6d18e20a9a1","tid":1217923,"uid":97383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人有同樣經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7986547e774f41db84e7ae8f7af33f5bbf3d16d7","tid":1217923,"uid":54303,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"2e243bbdad0f62804de138337cd9e6d18e20a9a1","tid":1217923,"uid":97383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人有同樣經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"屌你仲用中移動 全連登都杯緊中資啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fbce9da4ef9208b8a57d4a5cc0e4c557fd64c1","tid":1217923,"uid":43575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"好人好姐用咩支那移動呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bef763cff1f247b9a649c7e491907ac0169793","tid":1217923,"uid":97383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14fbce9da4ef9208b8a57d4a5cc0e4c557fd64c1","tid":1217923,"uid":43575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"好人好姐用咩支那移動呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"準備轉架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81aa9da1bb9692687056d48fc305d19a31ae62c","tid":1217923,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"搭錯線 時不時有 勾咗線你就唔會知"},{"pid":"ca10fd64153377dd966ed0fbee57c0e724ea4e6a","tid":1217923,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:35:18.000Z","msg":"俾多少少轉台啦"},{"pid":"19031f8d6469ed0c0f4e2b4dd1df602c1d788667","tid":1217923,"uid":97383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c81aa9da1bb9692687056d48fc305d19a31ae62c","tid":1217923,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"搭錯線 時不時有 勾咗線你就唔會知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"但係搭錯線嘅話我個fd仲聽到我講野架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986b0ca41376ba408fb124476fb25ba003aac77d","tid":1217923,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"搭錯線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b6ffc5d613aabfed6de73130820cc5a75e1b5a","tid":1217923,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19031f8d6469ed0c0f4e2b4dd1df602c1d788667","tid":1217923,"uid":97383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c81aa9da1bb9692687056d48fc305d19a31ae62c","tid":1217923,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT